# KAPiTaN OS — reprepro global options
#
# verbose            : extra logging in CI (helps debug publish failures).
# basedir .          : reprepro operates relative to the repo root (this dir's parent).
# ask-passphrase     : never set — CI passes the passphrase via gpg-agent/loopback.
# outdir / distdir / dbdir : defaults are fine for the Pages layout (pool/ + dists/).
#
# We do NOT enable "Acquire-By-Hash" at the reprepro layer for alpha; the publish
# workflow uploads pool/ BEFORE dists/ to avoid the CDN hash-mismatch window.

verbose
basedir .
